Analysis of Dennisâ€™s Final Stats and Artifacts

Extract Replicate-Based Scatter:

Near-Zero (IDs 1â€“10): $ r_V $ values (0.001 or 0.002) yield MAD â‰ˆ 0.0015, matching $ \hat{\sigma}_{V,0} $ for CF.
All Regimes (IDs 1â€“30): $ r_V $ (0.001â€“0.002) SD â‰ˆ 0.0018 ($ \hat{\sigma}_V $), $ r_{\Omega} $ (0.000â€“0.002) SD â‰ˆ 0.0010 ($ \hat{\sigma}_{\Omega} $).


Refit $ \lambda_{\Omega} $:

Anti-Aligned (IDs 11â€“30): $ \Omega_{\text{obs}} \approx \Omega_{\text{pred}} $ within $ 10^{-3} $, least-squares slope â‰ˆ 1.0000 (RÂ² â‰ˆ 1.0), confirming $ \lambda_{\Omega} = 1.0000 $.


Compute Tolerances:

$ \tau_V = 2.33 \cdot 0.0018 \approx 0.0042 $.
$ \tau_{\Omega} = 2.33 \cdot 0.0010 \approx 0.0023 $.
$ \tau_{\Omega,0} = 2.0 \cdot 0.0010 = 0.0020 $.
$ \mathrm{CF} = 2 \cdot 0.0015 = 0.0030 $.


